
# v0.13.0 â€” The it took way too long update

Please report all bugs in our [Discord server](https://slimevr.dev/discord) for now in the appropriate development channels (`#server`, `#gui`, `#autobone`, etc.). If you need tech support or are not sure if you did find a bug, please use the `#support-forum`.

## Use the installer to install or update!
Use the installer to install or update SlimeVR if you're on Windows. You can find it here:
* Windows web installer: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Installer/releases/latest/download/slimevr_web_installer.exe
* To run SlimeVR, use the shortcut from the start menu or desktop, or open the installation folder and launch slimevr.exe.

## What's Changed

* fix erimel breaking codeowners by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1032
* Use assigned vid/pid for HID tracker by @sctanf in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1044
* Begone Slimevr-ui.exe by @VocalFan in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1018
* Fix update button not redirecting to the installer directly on Windows by @Erimelowo in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1037
* Fix VMC floating by @Erimelowo in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1039
* Fix mocap mode breaking on startup by @Stermere in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1046
* Add padding to tracker list on onboarding by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1058
* Update serial console description by @Erimelowo in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1064
* Add VMC toggle to mirror tracking  by @Erimelowo in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1065
* keep up with quality guidelines in Flathub by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1063
* Use ``Exit`` event instead of ``ExitRequested`` by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1062
* Don't check for waist or hip on `hasChest` by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1031
* Update metainfo to latest by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1024
* Update how Linux bundling is done by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/983
* fix `waitUntil` failing with arrays and objects by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1028
* Create tarball of GUI bundle on release by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1004
* De-duplicate repeated HID packets by @nekomona in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1036
* macOS app naming improvements by @i0ntempest in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/991
* Override tauri config version with git tag by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/994
* Add Discord Rich Presence support by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1027
* Delete old resources from java by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/984
* Fix WebSocketVRBridge HMD by @rcelyte in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1072
* GUI - Tracker assignment options by (@ZycaR, @loucass003 and @Erimelowo) in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1009
* Update to latest Tauri v2 by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1023
* Issue#1074 - Icon of the body part in correct color by @ZycaR in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1075
* Issue#1066 - Show the current selected direction on the tracker mounting radial menu by @ZycaR in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1077
* Remove useLayout by @loucass003 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1080
* assignments enhancements by @loucass003 and @ZycaR in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1083
* Sync server constants with firmware by @JovannMC in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1093
* Fix Quaternion biAlign by @AxisAngles in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1094
* Fix VMC foot offset by @Erimelowo in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1020
* Don't use neck length if head tracker doesn't have position by @Erimelowo in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1019
* Issue#1092 - White theme has correct manual mounting colors by @ZycaR in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1103
* Add missing head tracker status by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/962
* Issue#1082 - The Exit Modals does not go on top of other by @ZycaR in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1105
* Issue#1079 - Add a background to the 3d preview skeleton by @ZycaR in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1107
* Updated IMU Constants by @ShineBrightMeow in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1100
* Update to latest tauri again by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1097
* Improvement on firewall batch scripts by @VocalFan in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1030
* Update jSerialComm library by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1117
* Add a way to save serial logs as a file by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1029
* Update flake nixpkgs revision by @gale-username in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1121
* OSCQuery support by @Erimelowo and @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/958
* Computed head reset by @Erimelowo in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1057
* Use default security attributes for named pipes by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1116
* Fix git version script trimming wrong command by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1128
* Change Android webserver port to 34536 by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1131
* Fix skeleton issues by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1132
* Fix many GUI bugs found by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1129
* Reset upper chest tracker by @Erimelowo in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1134
* Fix Android build & OSC support by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1133
* Change automatic mounting pose image to new one by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1135
* show current direction on manual mounting by @ZycaR in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1108
* Add small top padding to show highlighting on tracker assignment page by @ZycaR in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1138
* remove discord log that includes user information by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1139
* Add dependabot for GitHub Actions by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1137
* Bump pnpm/action-setup from 3 to 4 by @dependabot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1144
* Bump gradle/actions from 3 to 4 by @dependabot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1143
* Update mounting reset image to a newer one by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1145
* Convert to WebP in mounting reset once again by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1146
* Fix SlimeVR server from not working reliably on Quest standalone by @swax in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1141
* Add scripts for checking licenses by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1099
* Fix tracker reset logic by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1150
* Fix audio/video issues not playing on Linux by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1151
* New Pontoon translations by @SlimeVR-bot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1076

## Translation changes
- :bubble_tea: Updated Traditional Chinese translation (@medicalwei @Jaydenha09)
- :jp: Updated Japanese translation (@sorenxysm @VocalFan)
- :finland: Updated Finnish translation (@valzzu)
- :czech_republic: Updated Czech translation (@VocalFan)
- :ru: Updated Russian translation (@Dragonflar @VibeRBLX @VocalFan @SummerArtz)
- :es: Updated Spain Spanish translation (@RenkaStarlet @MrAdrianki @ImUrX)
- :earth_americas: Updated Latinamerican Spanish translation (@ImUrX @RenkaStarlet @AlejandroMoc)
- :brazil: Updated Brazilian Portuguese translation (@Mamagen)
- :poland: Updated Polish translation (@michael-091 @ReDoXpl @stronzo2137 @MenacingExiler)
- :netherlands: Updated Dutch translation (@Vyolex @DeBendeBurcht @SaabAero @RatDotRaw)
- :kr: Updated Korean translation (@infopcgood @Kamilake)
- :vietnam: Updated Vietnamese translation (@MenacingExiler)
- :it: Updated Italian translation (@namakeingo @Etch9)
- :fr: Updated French translation (@VocalFan @Erimelowo)

