__________

# v0.12.1 â€” The haunted mice update

Please report all bugs in our [Discord server](https://slimevr.dev/discord) for now in the appropriate development channels (`#server`, `#gui`, `#autobone`, etc.). If you need tech support or are not sure if you did find a bug, please use the `#support-forum`.

## Use the installer to install or update!
Use the installer to install or update SlimeVR if you're on Windows. You can find it here:
* Windows web installer: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Installer/releases/latest/download/slimevr_web_installer.exe
* To run SlimeVR, use the shortcut from the start menu or desktop, or open the installation folder and launch slimevr.exe.

### Flatpak distribution for Linux
Now you can install [SlimeVR from Flathub](https://flathub.org/apps/details/dev.slimevr.SlimeVR) and update it through there. You can install it by running: ``flatpak install flathub dev.slimevr.SlimeVR``

## What's Changed
* UDPPacket23RotationAndAcceleration: Switch x and y around to adjust for different axes by @9il in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1007
* Add more compact bundle protocol by @9il in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/999
* Change usb enumeration to only specific Vid/Pid by @sctanf in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1012
* Fix the HID decoding, replace Q14 with Q15, optimize by @9il in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1000
* don't toggle trackers if tracking is paused by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1013
* GUI - Fix condition for promise detection in a11y by @ZycaR in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1016
* fix macOS bundling action by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1015

## New Contributors
* @ZycaR made their first contribution in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1016

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/compare/v0.12.0...v0.12.1

__________

# v0.12.0 â€” The spring cleaning update

<img src="https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/assets/3698237/7b85bbe6-078d-4986-a0d1-fe49ce781da3" alt="gentle bingus" width="326" align="right" id="bingus-gentle">

Please report all bugs in our [Discord server](https://slimevr.dev/discord) for now in the appropriate development channels (`#server`, `#gui`, `#autobone`, etc.). If you need tech support or are not sure if you did find a bug, please use the `#support-forum`.

## Use the installer to install or update!
Use the installer to install or update SlimeVR if you're on Windows. You can find it here:
* Windows web installer: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Installer/releases/latest/download/slimevr_web_installer.exe
* To run SlimeVR, use the shortcut from the start menu or desktop, or open the installation folder and launch slimevr.exe.

### Flatpak distribution for Linux
Now you can install [SlimeVR from Flathub](https://flathub.org/apps/details/dev.slimevr.SlimeVR) and update it through there. You can install it by running: ``flatpak install flathub dev.slimevr.SlimeVR``

## What's Changed
* Complete TODO of replacing quatToXyzAngles with toEulerAngles by @VocalFan in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/915
* Prevent smoothing rollback by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/921
* Update CODEOWNERS for SolarXR by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/928
* Update FirmwareConstants.kt by @unlogisch04 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/927
* Add initial HID trackers support by @sctanf and @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/913
* don't send packets of bones we don't have by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/932
* Add linux files for CODEOWNERS by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/936
* Remove Futura from CODEOWNERS by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/935
* Update appstream metadata info by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/892
* Add tray support by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/897
* show drift compensation in tracker preview by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/937
* Change mounting position/rotation/direction to mounting orientation by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/939
* allow to set the socket dir via SLIMEVR_SOCKET_DIR by @Links2004 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/909
* Add pause tracking toggle to user action packet by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/922
* move biAlign into Quaternion.kt by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/940
* Fixing small bugs by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/924
* Migrate to pnpm by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/893
* Add Serial Console Wifi Scan by @unlogisch04 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/930
* Remove changing acceleration space in hid tracker by @sctanf in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/945
* Sleep if no HID device present by @sctanf in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/956
* Add an error boundary for WebGL by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/942
* Fix state bug on tray exit by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/944
* fastSeek is not available on most browsers, use currentTime by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/954
* Fix NaN rotation on reset with a zero quaternion by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/950
* Fix macOS bundling giving an error by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/943
* Update Kotlin and gradle plugins by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/957
* Allow multiple servers in the same network by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/900
* Connect one tracker at a time text adjustment by @ZRock35 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/965
* Make mounting reset follow headset rotation by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/953
* Improve autobone GUI steps by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/960
* Tpose down fix by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/967
* Use tauri store for GUI config by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/923
* Automatic SteamVR tracker switching by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/947
* Make ktmath object-less by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/959
* fix known devices not saving by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/969
* fix onboarding tracker connect description key by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/968
* Add network protocol version by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/972
* Update SolarXR to main branch by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/973
* Add Yaw Reset Smoothing by @nekomona in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/964
* Update to latest GUI dependencies by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/905
* Add toggle to save and load mounting reset by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/963
* fix tauri issues by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/977
* fix windows bundling not working by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/976
* Fix hands warning button styling by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/978
* Remove default keybind behavior in browser window by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/979
* Revert packages that are broken by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/980
* Make only search bar keybinds be prevented by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/981
* Add support for left/right steamvr toggles by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/982
* dont prefix `v` on versions by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/988
* assign knee when hasFoot for SteamVR by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/986
* fix permission issue on export proportions by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/987
* fix GUI visual bugs in autobone by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/985
* Support Datagrams up to 1472 bytes by @9il in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/998
* Fix missing space in BVH by @abb128 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/996
* Check if saved window size is at least the minimum allowed by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/993
* Add compact IMU frame (rot+acc) by @9il in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1001
* update hid4java to 0.8 by @ImUrX and @sctanf in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/992
* Update Github action versions to non-deprecated ones by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1005
* New Pontoon translations by @SlimeVR-bot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/914 [^1]

