1. Artwork made by @ButterscotchV [â†©](#bingus-gentle)


__________

# v0.12.0-rc.4

This is a release candidate. Back up your vrconfig.yml at `%AppData%\dev.slimevr.SlimeVR` before running.
Please report all bugs in our [Discord server](https://slimevr.dev/discord), in the appropriate forum post in `#beta-testing-forum`!

## Installation
* Download the new release below and extract it.
* Replace `slimevr.jar` and `slimevr.exe` in the install folder (`C:\Program Files (x86)\SlimeVR Server`)
* To run SlimeVR, use the shortcut from the start menu or desktop, or open the installation folder and launch slimevr.exe.

## What's Changed
* Support Datagrams up to 1472 bytes by @9il in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/998
* Fix missing space in BVH by @abb128 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/996
* Check if saved window size is at least the minimum allowed by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/993
* Add compact IMU frame (rot+acc) by @9il in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/1001
* update hid4java to 0.8 by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/992

## New Contributors
* @9il made their first contribution in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/998
* @abb128 made their first contribution in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/996

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/compare/v0.12.0-rc.3...v0.12.0-rc.4

__________

# v0.12.0-rc.3

This is a release candidate. Back up your vrconfig.yml at `%AppData%\dev.slimevr.SlimeVR` before running.
Please report all bugs in our [Discord server](https://slimevr.dev/discord), in the appropriate forum post in `#beta-testing-forum`!

## Installation
* Download the new release below and extract it.
* Replace `slimevr.jar` and `slimevr.exe` in the install folder (`C:\Program Files (x86)\SlimeVR Server`)
* To run SlimeVR, use the shortcut from the start menu or desktop, or open the installation folder and launch slimevr.exe.

## What's Changed
* dont prefix `v` on versions by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/988
* assign knee when hasFoot for SteamVR by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/986
* fix permission issue on export proportions by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/987
* fix GUI visual bugs in autobone by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/985

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/compare/v0.12.0-rc.2...v0.12.0-rc.3

