# v0.12.0-rc.2

This is a release candidate. Back up your vrconfig.yml at `%AppData%\dev.slimevr.SlimeVR` before running.
Please report all bugs in our [Discord server](https://slimevr.dev/discord), in the appropriate forum post in `#beta-testing-forum`!

## Installation
* Download the new release below and extract it.
* Replace `slimevr.jar` and `slimevr.exe` in the install folder (`C:\Program Files (x86)\SlimeVR Server`)
* To run SlimeVR, use the shortcut from the start menu or desktop, or open the installation folder and launch slimevr.exe.

## What's Changed
* fix tauri issues by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/977
* fix windows bundling not working by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/976
* Fix hands warning button styling by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/978
* Remove default keybind behavior in browser window by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/979
* Revert packages that are broken by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/980
* Make only search bar keybinds be prevented by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/981
* Add support for left/right steamvr toggles by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/982

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/compare/v0.12.0-rc.1...v0.12.0-rc.2

