# v0.12.0-rc.1

This is a release candidate. Back up your vrconfig.yml at `%AppData%\dev.slimevr.SlimeVR` before running.
Please report all bugs in our [Discord server](https://slimevr.dev/discord), in the appropriate forum post in `#beta-testing-forum`!

## Installation
* Download the new release below and extract it.
* Replace `slimevr.jar` and `slimevr.exe` in the install folder (`C:\Program Files (x86)\SlimeVR Server`)
* To run SlimeVR, use the shortcut from the start menu or desktop, or open the installation folder and launch slimevr.exe.

## What's Changed
* Complete TODO of replacing quatToXyzAngles with toEulerAngles by @VocalFan in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/915
* Prevent smoothing rollback by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/921
* Update CODEOWNERS for SolarXR by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/928
* Update FirmwareConstants.kt by @unlogisch04 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/927
* Add initial HID trackers support by @sctanf in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/913
* don't send packets of bones we don't have by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/932
* Add linux files for CODEOWNERS by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/936
* Remove Futura from CODEOWNERS by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/935
* Update appstream metadata info by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/892
* Add tray support by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/897
* show drift compensation in tracker preview by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/937
* Change mounting position/rotation/direction to mounting orientation by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/939
* allow to set the socket dir via SLIMEVR_SOCKET_DIR by @Links2004 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/909
* Add pause tracking toggle to user action packet by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/922
* move biAlign into Quaternion.kt by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/940
* Fixing small bugs by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/924
* Migrate to pnpm by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/893
* Add Serial Console Wifi Scan by @unlogisch04 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/930
* Remove changing acceleration space in hid tracker by @sctanf in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/945
* Sleep if no HID device present by @sctanf in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/956
* Add an error boundary for WebGL by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/942
* Fix state bug on tray exit by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/944
* fastSeek is not available on most browsers, use currentTime by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/954
* Fix NaN rotation on reset with a zero quaternion by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/950
* Fix macOS bundling giving an error by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/943
* Update Kotlin and gradle plugins by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/957
* Allow multiple servers in the same network by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/900
* Connect one tracker at a time text adjustment by @ZRock35 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/965
* Make mounting reset follow headset rotation by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/953
* Improve autobone GUI steps by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/960
* Tpose down fix by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/967
* Use tauri store for GUI config by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/923
* Automatic SteamVR tracker switching by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/947
* Make ktmath object-less by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/959
* fix known devices not saving by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/969
* fix onboarding tracker connect description key by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/968
