# v0.10.0

Please report all bugs in our [Discord server](https://slimevr.dev/discord) for now in the appropriate development channels (`#server`, `#gui`, `#autobone`, etc.). If you need tech support or are not sure if you did find a bug, please use the `#support-forum`.

## Use the installer to install or update!
Use the installer to install or update SlimeVR if you're on Windows. You can find it here:
* Windows web installer: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Installer/releases/latest/download/slimevr_web_installer.exe
* To run SlimeVR, use the shortcut from the start menu or desktop, or open the installation folder and launch slimevr.exe.

### ~~Flatpak distribution for Linux~~
Flatpak is not being updated because our framework is using an old version of `webkit2gtk` at the moment, we will update it when our framework releases a more stable release that supports the new version.

## What's Changed
* Update metainfo by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/834
* Convert HumanSkeleton to Kotlin by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/783
* add import proportions button by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/811
* Make UDPPackets Floats safe by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/832
* Fix config shenanigans by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/836
* knee-ankle interpolation by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/780
* Fix icons and add more & fill in web manifest by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/835
* Track connection by SocketAddress instead of IP address. by @kitlith in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/753
* Resets settings by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/806
* use devenv for nix develop by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/830
* Fix right foot skeleton offset by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/840
* Fix hash diplayName to not change by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/841
* Fix foot tracker orientation by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/843
* Android ByteBuffer and Color fixes by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/842
* Filter out !isSiteLocalAddress from addresses by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/847
* Add _trackerNum to extensions' displaynames by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/848
* Fix RPCUtil not checking for the interface before looking for it by @ImUrX in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/849
* feat: use path-alias by @marcozzxx810 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/771
* New Pontoon translations by @SlimeVR-bot in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/839

