# v0.10.0-rc.2

This is a release candidate. Back up your vrconfig.yml at `%AppData%\dev.slimevr.SlimeVR` before running.
Please report all bugs in our [Discord server](https://slimevr.dev/discord), in the appropriate forum post in `#beta-testing-forum`!

## Installation
* Download the new release below and extract it.
* Replace `slimevr.jar` and `slimevr.exe` in the install folder (`C:\Program Files (x86)\SlimeVR Server`)
* To run SlimeVR, use the shortcut from the start menu or desktop, or open the installation folder and launch slimevr.exe.

## What's Changed
* Fix right foot skeleton offset by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/840
* Fix hash diplayName to not change by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/841
* Fix foot tracker orientation by @Louka3000 in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/843
* Android ByteBuffer and Color fixes by @ButterscotchV in https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/pull/842


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/SlimeVR/SlimeVR-Server/compare/v0.10.0-rc.1...v0.10.0-rc.2

__________

